on 9/16/03 09:30, Snoopy related:

> Does anyone know the size of the valve adjusting screw for a 2L? I just
> received a set from a vendor that were 10MM  and they are way too big!!!  I
> need to know the correct size so I have the info in hand when calling..
> 
> Thanks in advance.
> 
> Snoopy

there are two sizes for adjusting screws - 10mm and 8mm. most 2l motors are
10mm, but it is possible to have a stock 2l with 8mm screws.

